               <msContents>
                  <summary>The Ms. contains the following texts: &#xD; I) Gadla Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi
                     "Vita of Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi" / (fols. 3ra-46ra l.1) &#xD; II) Ṭǝntä lǝdätomu
                     la-mänäkosat "Origin of the Monks" (fols. 46ra l. 2-46va l.10), in Amharic&#xD;
                     III) Malkǝʾa Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi "Image of Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi" (fols. 46va
                     l.11-49vb)&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
